channel.title: Need help
channel.description:
When ever I try to log in it says error connection to server. I think I know what caused this, I went on vacation so i gave my friend the source and the files so he can host it, then when I got home from vacation and he deletes the files I gave him now I cant get server up.
If you need a screen shot just ask me.
PLEASE HELP!

item.title: Need help
item.dc:creator: @Camballer Camballer
item.description:
@Camballer wrote:

Reconnect to your router go to where you porforwarded, then go to the cmd of your computer type in ipconfig look for ipv4 adress, check the last 3 digits, then where you portforwarded , if the ipv4 adress changed while you were gone, update it, simply by putting in the new one. EX: 192.168.1.101
